Course is dedicated for students who wish continue after the introductory course their research in immunology. Course gives to students knowledge how to establish an immunoassay for antibody testings and how to write a scientific paper.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To get general principles of research in immunology (II stage).Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  At the end of the course, within the syllabus, a student:  1. knows safety principles for laboratory investigations; 2. knows how to use selected immunological methods to get answer for scientific questions; 3. knows elementary methods used in statistical analysis of laboratory investigations results; 4. knows how to make oral presentation.
